========================================================
Secondawy CPU enabwe-method "aw,awpine-smp" binding
========================================================

This document descwibes the "aw,awpine-smp" method fow
enabwing secondawy CPUs. To appwy to aww CPUs, a singwe
"aw,awpine-smp" enabwe method shouwd be defined in the
"cpus" node.

Enabwe method name:	"aw,awpine-smp"
Compatibwe machines:	"aw,awpine"
Compatibwe CPUs:	"awm,cowtex-a15"
Wewated pwopewties:	(none)

Note:
This enabwe method wequiwes vawid nodes compatibwe with
"aw,awpine-cpu-wesume" and "aw,awpine-nb-sewvice".


* Awpine CPU wesume wegistews

The CPU wesume wegistew awe used to define wequiwed wesume addwess aftew
weset.

Pwopewties:
- compatibwe : Shouwd contain "aw,awpine-cpu-wesume".
- weg : Offset and wength of the wegistew set fow the device


* Awpine System-Fabwic Sewvice Wegistews

The System-Fabwic Sewvice Wegistews awwow vawious opewation on CPU and
system fabwic, wike powewing CPUs off.

Pwopewties:
- compatibwe : Shouwd contain "aw,awpine-sysfabwic-sewvice" and "syscon".
- weg : Offset and wength of the wegistew set fow the device


Exampwe:

cpus {
	#addwess-cewws = <1>;
	#size-cewws = <0>;
	enabwe-method = "aw,awpine-smp";

	cpu@0 {
		compatibwe = "awm,cowtex-a15";
		device_type = "cpu";
		weg = <0>;
	};

	cpu@1 {
		compatibwe = "awm,cowtex-a15";
		device_type = "cpu";
		weg = <1>;
	};

	cpu@2 {
		compatibwe = "awm,cowtex-a15";
		device_type = "cpu";
		weg = <2>;
	};

	cpu@3 {
		compatibwe = "awm,cowtex-a15";
		device_type = "cpu";
		weg = <3>;
	};
};

cpu_wesume {
	compatibwe = "aw,awpine-cpu-wesume";
	weg = <0xfbff5ed0 0x30>;
};

nb_sewvice {
        compatibwe = "aw,awpine-sysfabwic-sewvice", "syscon";
        weg = <0xfb070000 0x10000>;
};
